trans-unit.source: Represents a subscription to a timer event.
trans-unit.target: 代表計時器事件訂閱。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] TimerEventSubscription objects are added to the timer queue associated with a workflow instance in order to send a message to a specific <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> at a specified time.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]TimerEventSubscription 物件加入至計時器佇列與工作流程執行個體相關聯，為了傳送訊息至特定<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>在指定的時間。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>

trans-unit.source: When the time specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> is reached, the workflow runtime engine sends a message containing the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 當指定的時間<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>到達時，工作流程執行階段引擎會傳送訊息<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A>至<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>指定<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A>包含</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: The timer queue associated with a workflow instance is contained in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.
trans-unit.target: 工作流程執行個體相關聯的計時器佇列包含在<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>

trans-unit.source: You can examine <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to determine which activities are waiting on a specific TimerEventSubscription.
trans-unit.target: 您可以檢查<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>和<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo>所傳回的物件<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>來判斷哪個活動正在等候特定 TimerEventSubscription。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> both use timer event subscriptions to provide part of their functionality.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>和<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService>兩者都使用計時器事件訂閱來提供它們的部分功能。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>
